{"tid":1856353,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"中共勒令停拍影視節目, 劉偉強新戲傳有外籍人員發燒送院","createTime":"2020-02-01T14:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T15:28:22.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f3ccc11173f68bc9a053f9f20e4ffcf878149c","tid":1856353,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200201/LPW3OPM6L26UVNYGIOJ3DYWTWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200201%2FLPW3OPM6L26UVNYGIOJ3DYWTWM%2F&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=5c8edb99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200201%2FLPW3OPM6L26UVNYGIOJ3DYWTWM%2F&h=69cb474c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200201/LPW3OPM6L26UVNYGIOJ3DYWTWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】大陸勒令停拍影視節目 劉偉強新戲傳有外籍人員發燒送院<br />\n2小時前<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情不停在大陸擴散，大陸影視官方組織已發出通知，表示在疫情防控期間，所有影視製片公司、影視劇組及影視演員，應按照有關規定，暫停所有拍攝工作。如有影視公司、影視劇集在此期間因未暫停拍攝工作而引發疫情傳播，有關單位將承擔相關責任。在疫情期間，影視制片從業人員、影視演員亦有權拒絕拍攝工作。劉偉強做總導演的戰爭電影《冰雪長津湖》，原定今日在遼寧省丹東市開拍，但最後亦要解散劇組。<br />\n<br />\n有傳《冰》中曾有一名外籍工作人員在開拍前出現發燒，懷疑染上武漢肺炎，今日《蘋果》向劉偉強求證，他表示：「呢位外籍工作人員唔係武漢肺炎，只係傷風感冒，佢已經冇事返咗美國啦！戲組解散晒，我已經叫啲工作人員返屋企！我自己都返咗香港，咁大嘅疫情整個影視行業都受影響，唔係得部戲受損失，而家大家應該團結一心，共度時艱去戰勝呢場仗。」<br />\n<br />\n《冰》要趕今年國慶上映，原本拍攝時間已經緊迫，如今受疫情影響，劉偉強也不知何時可以開工，該片主演是吳京、易烊千璽和李冰冰等，由博納投資，故事是講述1950年韓戰爆發，大陸以志願軍抗美援朝。"},{"pid":"e6796b254f2a828fb195e329e5c0d0ab32158e9e","tid":1856353,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:42:30.000Z","msg":"認真, 大陸電影業唯一救亡方法, 係設立電影分級制, 開放拍攝三級色情片.<br />\n當年南韓電影可以翻生, 色情電影都有一部分功勞.  (係AV世代, 三級色情片依然有市場; Fifty Shades電影系列依然全球賣座!)<br />\n<br />\n我認真提示中共無所謂, 因為中共一定唔聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (正如中共都唔會聽老鼠曾既建議)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200127/2B324WLFINWSTRMTAO5H5DIUZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200127%2F2B324WLFINWSTRMTAO5H5DIUZU%2F&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=ea3198e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200127%2F2B324WLFINWSTRMTAO5H5DIUZU%2F&h=d8dd3258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200127/2B324WLFINWSTRMTAO5H5DIUZU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>《蘋果》訪問了北京某院線高層張先生，他估計春節後最少有100間戲院會因經濟問題倒閉：「之前好多戲院已經入座率低，已經好難維持，現在又來一個武漢肺炎，也不知道戲院何時可以重開，不少院商寧願選擇結業，而影視公司因沒戲開，相信會有不少公司相繼倒閉，因為這個疫情，全國的影視人員都幾乎全部停工，也不知要停多久才可以復工。2020年對中國影視行業肯定是十分艱難的一年，不倒閉也可能出現大量裁員潮。」</em></strong>"},{"pid":"cdd6bc871d78f45f9bb5e0270308fdf6b1602ba2","tid":1856353,"uid":313584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我認真提示中共無所謂, 因為中共一定唔聽 <br />\n (正如中共都唔會聽老鼠曾既建議)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f734726001435a3889240f8836180e3c38c8b01f","tid":1856353,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdd6bc871d78f45f9bb5e0270308fdf6b1602ba2","tid":1856353,"uid":313584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:46:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我認真提示中共無所謂, 因為中共一定唔聽 <br />\n (正如中共都唔會聽老鼠曾既建議)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:49:01.000Z","msg":"維尼表面上好強硬, 其實好蠢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n金融時報: 香港親共派也漸漸對習近平政府感到失望.  因為香港親共派一直力勸習近平政府以靈活手法解決香港問題, 但習近平政府一直拒絕接受意見, 只願照舊保持強硬.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1831582/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1831582/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"85ec66da9c6abc608151dda82117b0573d08a135","tid":1856353,"uid":81140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"又拍打J片"},{"pid":"6a8d7703f9956a65abe49605308adf75e746253f","tid":1856353,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85ec66da9c6abc608151dda82117b0573d08a135","tid":1856353,"uid":81140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"又拍打J片"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"&quot;抗美援朝&quot;<br />\n<br />\n反美國既打J片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f15b1a8c9ac23e902d6350c0855a429170e23a8","tid":1856353,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"「罷工」港龍員工需要支持！請幫忙宣傳！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856363</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dd17e2584dfacbcf5495b17ce6674d53628bea5a","tid":1856353,"uid":81140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a8d7703f9956a65abe49605308adf75e746253f","tid":1856353,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85ec66da9c6abc608151dda82117b0573d08a135","tid":1856353,"uid":81140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"又拍打J片"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"&quot;抗美援朝&quot;<br />\n<br />\n反美國既打J片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca5e79c1757d94b67fdab31b8